# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : owl:intersectionOf (class intersection)

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### Jane is both a Worker and a Parent, and WorkingParent is their
### intersection -> Jane must be typed WorkingParent.
:IntersectionOf_Jane rdf:type :IntersectionOf_WorkingParent .
